{"id": "1506228208696037407", "channel_id": "1506228208696037407", "author_id": "1430361164029624460", "author_name": "salami_87", "content": "I have a quick question about mechanics. Why do Twice Posse and Tawil's Posse only count as a single stack for Gramona and 24 Chaos's passives? Shouldn't Twice Posse count as a double proc, and Tawil's Posse count as selecting another pose within the Posse?\"", "timestamp": "2026-05-19T09:33:09.320000+00:00", "thread_id": "1506228208696037407", "attachments": [{"id": "1506228209488756756", "filename": "Screenrecorder-2026-05-19-04-24-46-216.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 7358768, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506228208696037407/1506228209488756756/Screenrecorder-2026-05-19-04-24-46-216.mp4?ex=6a0d7fd5&is=6a0c2e55&hm=61640487b6247c90afb0c1d283c47ce2df15a7c68c6e0408ef2e8341c03a6428&"}, {"id": "1506228210902503494", "filename": "Screenrecorder-2026-05-19-04-15-47-331.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 3953104, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506228208696037407/1506228210902503494/Screenrecorder-2026-05-19-04-15-47-331.mp4?ex=6a0d7fd5&is=6a0c2e55&hm=5accf243a9e8d5c8fc161f776ccaf5074acf77df7efe2c5953e2d92250cd99c8&"}]}
{"id": "1506235448194764890", "channel_id": "1506228208696037407", "author_id": "1025896862210859028", "author_name": "mayhemvt", "content": "Speculation from how I understand it\n\n- Silver Key Dawn: You cast the posse once, the effects just happen to double. \n\n- Tawil: Her posse just essentially becomes \"Chosen Posse + Keyflare\". It's not really casting another Posse so much as it is yoinking the effects like her Exalt does with cards.", "timestamp": "2026-05-19T10:01:55.351000+00:00", "thread_id": "1506228208696037407"}
{"id": "1506217086630891520", "channel_id": "1506217086630891520", "author_id": "1160510535670968330", "author_name": "yeriko703", "content": "A few ideas i'd like to see in the game\n\n1. Training mode. Simply dummy pretty please <:please:1356053110375714817> \n\nThe game's difficulty increases along with players skill levels, but we still don't have a training ground to see how some parts of game work. Most often, we have to test in dtide or Story Mode, which isn't the best place for testing\n\n2. More cosmetics for a donation\nPfp, emoute, avatar frame\n\n3. Black Offering  \ndtide is already a familiar, updated content for all players, but what if you can't complete it? You're simply losing important currency and depriving yourself of access to 4 SSR and a lot SR wheels. It would be great to be able to get them regardless of whether you've completed dtide or not(d-jewel on black offering) \n\n4. New endgame content\nMany 3d gacha games have \"Tower\", where our tower? xdx One fight(like elite fight in story mode), no relics, no gnosis, at each new stage new enemies appear and their level increases. What about reward? Pure cores and some resource <:question2:1356053130336272414>  Every 5(?) stages elite fight, every 10(?) stages final boss fight(from every arcs(On the lower floors there are arc1 bosses, on the floors above there are bosses from all arcs) and 5-10(?) pure cores. There is also a leaderboard with those who climbed to the highest level", "timestamp": "2026-05-19T08:48:57.613000+00:00", "thread_id": "1506217086630891520", "reactions": [{"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1356053116260454534", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1506217086979014786", "filename": "130159904_p5_master1200.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 487237, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506217086630891520/1506217086979014786/130159904_p5_master1200.jpg?ex=6a0d7579&is=6a0c23f9&hm=10003697fccffc281e144729590c300162f377151acf3729939f082ca4646cf1&"}]}
